From: Pritzker, Tom 
Sent: 8/8/2016 9:28:25 PM 
To: jeffrey E. [jeeyacation@gmail.com] 
Subject: RE: Re: 
Importance: High 
You have to be a bit of a wonk to know some of the names, but Nye, Scowcroft and Nick Burns run it (Scowcroft being 
replaced by Condi). Members include Patraeus, Albright, Slaughter, Donalon (Obama NSA), Hadley (Bush NSA), Sullivan 
(NSA Hillary), Bill Burns (State #2), Kurt Campbell, Hoss Carwright (#2 it Chiefs), Harman, Ignatius, Sanger, Nunn, Reed, 
Sawers (M16), Sherman (iran deal), Work (current #2 DoD). It seems to now be taking on an aura. 
Looking for a time to come catch up in NY. 
From: jeffrey E. [mailto:jeevacation@gmail.com] 
Sent: Monday, August 08, 2016 2:45 PM 
To: Pritzker, Tom 
Subject: Re: 
who attends 
On Mon, Aug 8, 2016 at 1:39 PM, Pritzker, Tom -.11111=> wrote: 
I'm working on a date. Just finished presentation on leadership to grand pooh baahs of Aspen Strategy 
Group. Take a look at members it will make you laugh. Certainly made me laugh when they asked me to do 
it.
